title: Adafruit DAC7578 Breakout Schematic
summary: Complete board schematic for the Adafruit DAC7578 breakout with power supply conditioning, I2C pull-ups/level-shift support, status LED, DAC7578 IC, and STEMMA QT connectors.

structured_data.description: Schematic shows DAC7578 converting I2C commands into eight analog outputs (VOUTA through VOUTH), with breakout headers and STEMMA QT connectors exposing power, I2C, and control signals.
